Find a partner…
who sees the good in you,
who loves you at your best and at your worst,
who accepts your flaws,
who helps you grow into the best you,
who loves your family like their own,
who makes you laugh and smile,
who cares for himself so he can care for you,
who doesn’t give up when the going gets tough,
who you respect, and
who respects you.
